# Azure Custom Role Designer Configuration

# OPTION 1: Use Azure CLI Authentication (Recommended)
# Just ensure you're logged in with: `az login`
# No configuration needed in this file

# OPTION 2: Use Service Principal Authentication
# Uncomment and fill in the values below
# AZURE_SUBSCRIPTION_ID=your-subscription-id-here
# AZURE_TENANT_ID=your-tenant-id-here
# AZURE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id-here
# AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret-here

# OPTION 3: Use Managed Identity (when running on Azure)
# No configuration needed; the library will automatically detect
